definitions.definition: ( Judaism ) The tenth month of the civil year and the fourth month of the ecclesiastical year in the Jewish calendar ,  after Sivan and before Av .

main_definition: ( Judaism ) The tenth month of the civil year and the fourth month of the ecclesiastical year in the Jewish calendar ,  after Sivan and before Av .

definitions.definition: A Sumerian god of food and vegetation .

main_definition: A Sumerian god of food and vegetation .
